FAQ

Got any questions?
We've got answers.

Got any questions?
We've got answers.

What services does Digimax Creatives offer?

We specialize in AI-powered website design, development, hosting, and ongoing management to help businesses establish a strong online presence.

How long does it take to build a website?

Project timelines vary based on complexity, but most websites are completed within 2-6 weeks.

Do you offer custom website designs or just templates?

We offer both! You can choose from our vast template library or opt for a fully custom design tailored to your brand.

Can I update my website after it's launched?

Yes! We provide user-friendly content management options, and we also offer ongoing maintenance services.

Is my website going to be mobile-friendly?

Absolutely! Every website we build is fully responsive and optimized for all devices.

Do you provide SEO services?

Yes, we integrate basic SEO best practices into all our websites, and we offer advanced SEO services upon request.

What kind of support do you offer after the website goes live?

We provide ongoing support, including updates, security monitoring, and technical assistance.

How do I get started?

Simply book a free consultation with us, and well discuss your needs to create the perfect website for your business.
